# GLIGEN Checkpoint Directory

This directory stores GLIGEN model checkpoints.

## Automatic Download (Recommended)

Checkpoints are automatically downloaded on first startup when:
- `GLIGEN_AUTO_DOWNLOAD_GENERATION=true` for generation model (default)
- `GLIGEN_AUTO_DOWNLOAD_INPAINTING=true` for inpainting model (default)
- `LOAD_GLIGEN=true`

Models download separately - only enable the ones you need!
No manual download needed!

## Manual Download (Alternative)

If auto-download is disabled, download manually:

1. Generation checkpoint:
   wget https://huggingface.co/gligen/gligen-generation-text-box/resolve/main/diffusion_pytorch_model.bin \
     -O checkpoint_generation_text.pth

2. Inpainting checkpoint:
   wget https://huggingface.co/gligen/gligen-inpainting-text-box/resolve/main/diffusion_pytorch_model.bin \
     -O checkpoint_inpainting_text.pth

## Docker Usage

In docker-compose.yml, mount this directory as a volume:
  volumes:
    - gligen_checkpoints:/app/app/external/GLIGEN/gligen_checkpoints

This ensures checkpoints persist between deployments and are only downloaded once.
